# 📈 FX-Algo-Sentinel V1
### *Automated Precision Trading Engine using Python and MQL5*

---

## 📄 Project Overview
Huu ni mfumo wa kisasa wa kujiendesha (**Algorithmic Trading System**) ulioundwa maalum kwa ajili ya soko la Forex. Mradi huu unalenga kuondoa mihemko (emotions) wakati wa kufanya maamuzi ya kibiashara kwa kutumia kanuni madhubuti za **Price Action** na **Market Structure**. 

Mfumo huu unachanganua chati kwa muda halisi (Real-time), unatambua fursa, na kufanya miamala (Execution) kulingana na vigezo vilivyowekwa bila kuhitaji usimamizi wa binadamu wa kila dakika.

---

## 🚀 Key Features
*   **🎯 Smart Entry Logic:** Inatumia mchanganyiko wa *Support/Resistance* na *Moving Averages* kutambua mwelekeo wa soko (Trend).
*   **🛡️ Advanced Risk Management:** Mfumo unapiga hesabu ya **Lot Size** moja kwa moja kulingana na asilimia ya mtaji (Equity %) ili kulinda akaunti.
*   **📈 Trailing Stop-Loss:** Inasogeza *Stop Loss* mbele soko linapoenda upande wa faida ili kuhakikisha faida haipotei.
*   **⚡ MT5 Integration:** Imeunganishwa moja kwa moja na **MetaTrader 5** kupitia Python API kwa ajili ya kasi na usahihi wa hali ya juu.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Tools
*   **Language:** ![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3776AB?style=flat&logo=python&logoColor=white)
*   **Libraries:** `MetaTrader5`, `Pandas`, `NumPy`, `Datetime`
*   **Platform:** MetaTrader 5 (MT5)
*   **Strategy:** Price Action & Algorithmic Execution

---

## ⚙️ How It Works
1. **Data Collection:** Bot inapata data za bei (OHLC) moja kwa moja kutoka kwenye terminal ya MT5.
2. **Analysis:** Inatumia *Moving Averages* na *RSI* kuchuja signal za uongo.
3. **Execution:** Signal ikipatikana, bot inatuma "Order" ya BUY au SELL ikiwa na *Stop Loss* na *Take Profit* tayari.
4. **Monitoring:** Inafuatilia trade mpaka ifungwe kwa faida au loss ndogo.

